Document: EditorSceneFormatImporter
Path: godot/classes/class_editorsceneformatimporter.rst
Summary: Defines an importer script for a third-party 3D format.

EditorSceneFormatImporter allows to define an importer script for a third-party 3D format.

To use EditorSceneFormatImporter, register it using the EditorPlugin.add_scene_importer_plugin() method first.
